Wl Ross & Co. LLC Revenue and Financial Data

   WL Ross & Co. is a friend to companies in need, indeed. A subsidiary of Invesco, the company specializes in improving the financial condition of distressed businesses by offering capital restructuring services and making direct private equity investments in such firms. The company also acts as advisor in restructurings, mergers and acquisitions, privatizations, and litigation cases. It has some $5 billion of assets under management on behalf of private investors in the US, Europe, and Asia. WL Ross focuses on the steel, coal, textile, health care, automotive, and financial services industries.
  







