Wilbur Ross

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Not to be confused with Wilburn K. Ross.


Wilbur Ross








39th United States Secretary of Commerce



Incumbent



Assumed office
February 28, 2017


